43
00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:14.030
including event-based, asynchronous communications,

44
00:02:14.030 --> 00:02:16.040
tracing and logging in the system,

45
00:02:16.040 --> 00:02:19.040
and various hybrid architectures.

46
00:02:19.040 --> 00:02:22.010
We'll finish up looking at the architecture choices

47
00:02:22.010 --> 00:02:25.040
you need to make, design considerations,

48
00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:27.030
