53
00:02:39.050 --> 00:02:41.060
This course will be fast-paced

54
00:02:41.060 --> 00:02:44.010
and loaded with industry examples,

55
00:02:44.010 --> 00:02:48.080
my personal experiences, and industry best practices.

56
00:02:48.080 --> 00:02:51.080
This in-depth conversation will leave you

57
00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:54.040
with a solid foundation for you

58
00:02:54.040 --> 00:02:57.020
and your team to make decisions

59
00:02:57.020 --> 00:02:59.080
about moving to this architectural model,

60
